				<td colspan="2"><span>A ton of bards are nowhere close to bagging their epics.  Those that can bag their epics are probably the higher-end raiders.  If Phinny, Fear, and Trak are all you have left, I'd go for the epic.  Phinny is soloable (due it with wizzy or something for a much easier time).  Fear takes time, but is soloable.  When my guild was after the Shissar, I'd go into Fear an hour before raid time and solo-break it.  
<br />

<br />
Two of your three pieces are easily doable, 1 requires help.  If your gear is what you described, it probably means you aren't a raider.  If you aren't a raider, the epic will provide very nice stats along with the instrument mods with a nice proc as a bonus.  
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
